  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. In a large bowl, combine bison ground meat, salt, pepper, and garlic powder. Mix well with your hands until just combined.",
    "3. Divide meat into 4-6 portions, depending on desired slider size.",
    "4. Grill meat for 3-4 minutes per side, or until cooked to your desired level of doneness.",
    "5. Meanwhile, toast brioche buns on the grill or in a toaster.",
    "6. Assemble sliders with a cooked patty, 1-2 slices of cheese, 1-2 slices of bacon, 1/4 cup of lettuce, 1/4 cup of tomato, and a dollop of mayonnaise.",
    "7. Serve immediately and enjoy!",
    "8. Optional: Top with caramelized onions or additional toppings of your choice."
